            <title>[LU-17871] FLOCK ownlocks may be not set</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17871</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Fixes LUS-10623/ &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15402&quot; title=&quot;Speedup flock read lock enqueue&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-15402&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-15402&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ldlm: speedup RD flock enqueue&lt;/p&gt;

